title: 1of1 Season
description:
Get yourselves and your wallets ready for the next huge 1/1 event party on TEZ! Mint only 1/1, 3 max per artist. Color theme: PINK x RED (use both colours or choose one). Setup an auction with a starting price between 30 & 70 xtz.
Add "1of1SZN" as a tag at mint time to be visible here.
